[[瑙魯|瑙魯]]是南[[太平洋|太平洋]]的一個島國，位於[[馬紹爾群島|馬紹爾群島]]南側，[[赤道|赤道]]以南{{convert|53|km}}。瑙魯的陸地面積只有{{convert|21|km2|abbr=on}}，海岸線長{{convert|30|km|mi|adj=mid|coastline}}。島嶼外側有環礁包圍<ref>{{cite web|author1=CIA factbook|title=Nauru Terrain - Geography|url=http://www.indexmundi.com/nauru/terrain.html|website=www.indexmundi.com|access-date=19 April 2016|archive-date=2018-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127064716/https://www.indexmundi.com/nauru/terrain.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。瑙魯的專屬經濟區面積有{{convert|308,480|km2|mi2|abbr=on}}，領海主張有12海里。

瑙魯屬於熱帶氣候，每年11月至2月是雨季。[[磷酸鹽|磷酸鹽]]是瑙魯唯一的礦業自然資源<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://creation.com/nauru-phosphate-deposits|title=Nauru phosphate deposits - creation.com|website=creation.com|language=en-gb|access-date=2019-06-24|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806014547/https://creation.com/nauru-phosphate-deposits|dead-url=no}}</ref>。漁業是瑙魯另一自然資源<ref>[http://www.wcpfc.int/sc4/pdf/Nauru%20Annual%20Report%20(Part%201)%20-%20SC4.pdf Annual Report Part 1: Information on Fisheries, Research and Statistics: Republic of Nauru.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wcpfc.int/sc4/pdf/Nauru%20Annual%20Report%20(Part%201)%20-%20SC4.pdf |date=20200703161415 }} Working Paper 17 of the 4th Scientific Committee of the Western and Central Pacific Fisheries Commission. WCPFC 2008.</ref>。瑙魯島上沒有任何河流及湖泊。
